  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK624">
<l>maṭuttavā yellām pakaṭaṉṉā ṉuṟṟa </l>
<l>viṭukka ṇiṭarppā ṭuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Troubles will vanish (i.e., will be troubled) before the man who (struggles against difficulties) as a buffalo (drawing a cart) through deep mire.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
